{"tid":1946474,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同男朋友個妹唔係幾玩得埋點搞？","createTime":"2020-03-27T15:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T16:34:34.000Z","uid":337102,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8e2bdbb01f87cf5e021a51305ddd1c0a4b099d","tid":1946474,"uid":337102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:51:06.000Z","msg":"一開始去佢屋企個陣幾好會一齊煲下戲<br />\n但後尾我同男朋友講唔想黎到淨係煲劇煲成日<br />\n之後就冇再一齊煲劇 所以就冇咩話題<br />\n然之後住多咗見佢啲態度同性格都有啲差<br />\n好似人哋幫佢做野/對佢好係老馮咁<br />\n對呀爸呀媽態度又勁差<br />\n性格同我男朋友跟本係相反<br />\n我為咗日後嘅日子唔想尷尬同希望佢唔會對我有敵意<br />\n因為佢之前都呷過我醋 佢哥第一次拍拖<br />\n我會成日特登搵兩句講下<br />\n平時上去都會買啲零食呀蛋糕呀上去 因為佢都中意食<br />\n佢呀爸呀媽對我都好好冇壓力<br />\n相反對住佢呀妹真係好大壓力<br />\n但又唔敢同男朋友講 始終佢哋本身都好close<br />\n而且我又唔想因為我嘅關係搞到佢哋關係差咗<br />\n而家唔可以出街 最多只可以去男朋友到住先見到佢<br />\n各位有咩建議可以俾下小妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSorry for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22329794a17be15dc921ba51884eae0adbdb5cdd","tid":1946474,"uid":153722,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"唔差就得啦<br />\n唔洗特登friend"},{"pid":"0ca5bbfc25c88c5033b88f7dac1a6d238baacdf2","tid":1946474,"uid":214644,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"佢本身冇仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n介紹比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61702e78d1ebeda0e6e24f64a704ba5f6b56c6d7","tid":1946474,"uid":237316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco